        public static java.util.LinkedHashMap analyzeChanges(JDBCVirtuosoRep jdbc,
                                     java.lang.String changesOntolSchema,
                                     java.lang.String datasetUri,
                                     java.lang.String v1,
                                     java.lang.String v2,
                                     java.lang.String changeType,
                                     boolean tempOntology)
                                              throws java.lang.Exception
        Provides statistical analysis by returning a map that contains the change name as key and the change occurrences as value
        Parameters:
        jdbc - the JDBCVirtuosoRep objects that creates internally the connection to the store
        changesOntolSchema - the changes ontology schema
        datasetUri - the selected dataset URI
        v1 - the selected old version
        v2 - the selected new version
        changeType - the type of changes to analyze ("Simple_Change","Complex_Change" or null for both cases)
        tempOntology - determines if results are located in a temp ontology (custom compare case)
        Returns:
        a map that contains the change name as key and the change occurrences as value
        Throws:
        java.lang.Exception - general exception
